{"word":"G2714 - κατενώπιον - katenṓpion - kat-en-o'-pee-on - Before","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατενώπιον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katenṓpion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-en-o'-pee-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Before</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சந்நிதி முன்பாக, முன்பாக - வினை யடை"},{"paragraph":"over against, opposite, before the face of, before the presence of, in the sight of, before"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G1799 - ἐνώπιον - enṓpion - en-o'-pee-on/1799\">G1799</a>; <i>directly in front of:</i> - before (the presence of), in the sight of.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}